---
---
<section id="stack" class="section">
  <div class="s-in">
    <div class="s-hd fu">
      <span class="eyebrow">The stack</span>
      <h2 class="split">Full-stack roots.<br>AI-native build.</h2>
      <p>The engineering depth is what makes the AI systems reliable. You can't build production agent systems without understanding the infrastructure underneath them.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stack-grid" data-stagger>
      <div class="sg-col spot">
        <div class="sg-title">AI &amp; Agents</div>
        <div class="sg-items">
          <div class="sg-item hi"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Claude API (Anthropic)</div>
          <div class="sg-item hi"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Model Context Protocol (MCP)</div>
          <div class="sg-item hi"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Multi-agent orchestration</div>
          <div class="sg-item hi"><span class="sg-dot"></span>RAG systems &amp; pgvector</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>LangChain / LlamaIndex</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>OpenAI API</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Prompt engineering &amp; evals</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Memory &amp; context systems</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sg-col spot">
        <div class="sg-title">Frontend &amp; Mobile</div>
        <div class="sg-items">
          <div class="sg-item hi"><span class="sg-dot"></span>React / Next.js</div>
          <div class="sg-item hi"><span class="sg-dot"></span>TypeScript</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>React Native</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Tailwind CSS</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Vue.js</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Redux / Zustand</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>REST &amp; GraphQL APIs</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Framer Motion</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sg-col spot">
        <div class="sg-title">Backend &amp; Infrastructure</div>
        <div class="sg-items">
          <div class="sg-item hi"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Ruby on Rails</div>
          <div class="sg-item hi"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Node.js / Python</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>PostgreSQL / Redis</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>HubSpot / Salesforce MCP</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>AWS / Railway / Render</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Sidekiq / job queues</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Webhooks &amp; event pipelines</div>
          <div class="sg-item"><span class="sg-dot"></span>Docker &amp; CI/CD</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
